---
/**
 * WhyBook.astro — "Why book with us" section. Zero JavaScript.
 * All content is static — no API calls needed.
 */
---

<section id="why-book" class="relative py-8 md:py-14">
  <!-- Background image layer -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-0">
    <div class="w-full h-full bg-center bg-cover" style="background-image: url('/Banner/Background.jpg')"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/75 md:bg-white/50"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-6 md:mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Why book with us</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-[#FAD502] mx-auto rounded-full mt-3"></div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm md:text-base">
        Trusted services tailored for Rome travellers — we make planning easy so you can focus on exploring.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-3 md:p-5 flex flex-col items-start gap-3 shadow-sm">
        <div class="bg-[#FAD502] text-[#930B31] p-2 md:p-3 rounded-full shadow-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M2 20h20L12 4z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm md:text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Rome-focused expertise</h3>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-600">Local knowledge and curated tours to make the most of your time in Rome.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-3 md:p-5 flex flex-col items-start gap-3 shadow-sm">
        <div class="bg-[#FAD502] text-[#930B31] p-2 md:p-3 rounded-full shadow-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm md:text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Trusted operators</h3>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-600">We partner with trusted local operators who prioritize safety and quality.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-3 md:p-5 flex flex-col items-start gap-3 shadow-sm">
        <div class="bg-[#FAD502] text-[#930B31] p-2 md:p-3 rounded-full shadow-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.82z"/><line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7" stroke="white" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm md:text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Transparent pricing</h3>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-600">No hidden fees — clear pricing and easy booking so you can book with confidence.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-3 md:p-5 flex flex-col items-start gap-3 shadow-sm">
        <div class="bg-[#FAD502] text-[#930B31] p-2 md:p-3 rounded-full shadow-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm md:text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Customer support</h3>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-600">Friendly support to help before, during, and after your trip.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
